<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5"> صحيح:</span> ق ـ مضى <span class="c2">(٤٧٨٥)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>